@page "/"
@using Web.Razor.Pages
@model IndexModel

@{
	ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<section class="hero fade-in" style="position:relative;">
	<div class="mq-container hero-content" style="position:relative; z-index:2;">
		<h1 class="t-display" style="max-width:980px; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,4.2vw,3.6rem); line-height:1.05;">
			Return to <span class="server-name-accent" style="white-space:nowrap;">Ook</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="t-lead" style="max-width:880px;">
			The Monkey King is gone, Ka's shadow still stirs, and five tribes stand ready: Sea Dragons, Chim Foo, Ootu Mystics, Ice Raiders and Mek‑Tek. Reclaim lost trails, master elements, craft gear and help rebuild a world full of secrets.
		</p>
		<div class="hero-stats" role="group" aria-label="Server statistics" style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
			<div class="stat-pill" aria-live="polite">Online: <strong>@Model.PlayerCount</strong></div>
			<div class="stat-pill">Registered: <strong>@Model.AccountCount</strong></div>
		</div>
		<div style="margin-top:var(--mq-space-5); display:flex; gap:18px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
			<a href="/en/signup" class="btn-modern btn-accent fx-pop btn-pad-lg" aria-label="Sign up and begin your journey">Create Your Monkey</a>
			<a href="/download" class="btn-modern btn-outline-jungle btn-pad-lg" aria-label="Download the launcher">Download Launcher</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; inset:0; background:radial-gradient(circle at 22% 32%,rgba(209,221,97,.20),transparent 60%), radial-gradient(circle at 78% 68%,rgba(232,163,46,.18),transparent 65%); opacity:.9; mix-blend-mode:overlay;"></div>
</section>

<section class="mq-container mt-space reveal" data-reveal>
	<div class="panel-glass panel-p-lg jungle-frame" style="--frame-accent:var(--mq-color-accent);">
		<h2 class="t-section" style="margin-top:0; font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.4vw,2.1rem); letter-spacing:.5px;">About Ook</h2>
		<p class="lead" style="font-size:.88rem; line-height:1.55; max-width:860px;">
			After the Monkey King's last stand against Ka, ruin and strange energy settled over trails and towns. Companions and builders rose up, shaping refuge out of wreckage. New monkeys now pick up the work: clearing shadow creatures, reopening highways and reviving tribe legacies.
		</p>
		<div class="vine-divider" style="margin:1.5rem 0;"></div>
		<p style="font-size:.78rem; line-height:1.55; max-width:880px;">
			Get gear, learn recipes, unlock movement tools and element powers while helping diplomats and founders' successors. Every trail pushed forward brings Ook closer to what it was—before Ka stirred again.
		</p>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="mq-container mt-space reveal" data-reveal>
	<div class="ui-card card-gradient-border" style="padding:2.25rem 2rem;">
		<div class="ui-card-header" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.75rem;">
			<span style="font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.5px;">The Five Tribes</span>
		</div>
		<div class="grid-auto" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
			<div class="feature-card" data-accent="amber">
				<h5 style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.4rem;">Sea Dragons</h5>
				<p style="font-size:.7rem; line-height:1.45;">Fire pirates of the Coconut Isles (Smugglers Highway). Founder Dragontail; Captain Blacktail now commands Dragontail Square.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card" data-accent="lime">
				<h5>Chim Foo</h5>
				<p style="font-size:.7rem; line-height:1.45;">Air ninjas in hidden Iron Mountain fortresses. Founded by Mist; Grand Master Whisper leads the order.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card" data-accent="mist">
				<h5>Ootu Mystics</h5>
				<p style="font-size:.7rem; line-height:1.45;">Earth sages of the Swamps (Fire Canyon Highway). Founded by Mama Ootu; Mama Babu now keeps the glades.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card" data-accent="lime">
				<h5>Ice Raiders</h5>
				<p style="font-size:.7rem; line-height:1.45;">Ice / water daredevils on the northern heights. Founded by Grapp; Sigthor holds the mantle.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card" data-accent="amber">
				<h5>Mek-Tek</h5>
				<p style="font-size:.7rem; line-height:1.45;">Inventors by Fire Canyon Highway. Founded by Trunket. Not joinable; famed for engineering (Clock Tower) and rumored lightning tech.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="mq-container mt-space reveal" data-reveal>
	<div class="grid-auto" style="--mq-space-4:2rem; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));">
		<div class="panel-glass panel-p-md fx-pop" style="position:relative;">
			<h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size:1rem; letter-spacing:.5px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:.4rem;">
				<span class="tribe-tag" data-tribe="amber">Questing</span>
			</h3>
			<p style="font-size:.8rem; line-height:1.5;">Ka's shadow minions have choked key trails, isolating regions and threatening trade. Yet these dangers open paths for fearless monkeys to earn renown, gear and experience as they liberate routes and aid allies.</p>
			<p style="font-size:.7rem; opacity:.75;">Allies across Ook eagerly trade rewards for your courage.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="panel-glass panel-p-md fx-pop" style="position:relative;">
			<h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size:1rem; letter-spacing:.5px;">
				<span class="tribe-tag" data-tribe="lime">Crafting</span>
			</h3>
			<p style="font-size:.8rem; line-height:1.5;">Why buy gear when you can make it? Recipes—found, rewarded or purchased—unlock tools, equipment and curios. Gather ingredients across zones and forge items directly from your Book of Recipes.</p>
			<p style="font-size:.7rem; opacity:.75;">Create for yourself, friends, or to barter.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="panel-glass panel-p-md fx-pop" style="position:relative;">
			<h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size:1rem; letter-spacing:.5px;">
				<span class="tribe-tag" data-tribe="mist">Bestiary</span>
			</h3>
			<p style="font-size:.8rem; line-height:1.5;">Shadow creatures and wild natives block trails and guard loot. Learn their patterns, earn materials and clear the way for tribe progress.</p>
			<p style="font-size:.7rem; opacity:.75;">Knowledge makes tougher fights easier.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section class="mq-container mt-space reveal" data-reveal>
	<div class="panel-glass panel-p-lg center" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.5rem;">
		<h2 style="margin:0; font-size:1.4rem; letter-spacing:.5px;">Ready to Return to Ook?</h2>
		<div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;">
			<a href="/en/signup" class="btn-modern btn-accent btn-pad-md fx-pop">Create Your Monkey</a>
			<a href="/download" class="btn-modern btn-outline-jungle btn-pad-md">Get the Launcher</a>
		</div>
		<p style="font-size:.7rem; opacity:.65; margin:0;">Fan remake project – not affiliated with the original publisher.</p>
	</div>
</section>
